  "detailed_description": "<h1>Workshop Support</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sandboxels now supports the Steam Workshop - Browse and publish saved canvases in-game!</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sandboxels</strong> is a  falling-sand game featuring heat simulation, electricity, density, chemical reactions, cooking, and fire spread. With over 500 unique elements to play with, Sandboxels is a great simulator to pass the time and relax.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664820/extras/57b5c3c1b485bedf31fe9ff30515c73b.avif?t=1772994627\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664820/extras_big/57b5c3c1b485bedf31fe9ff30515c73b.avif?t=1772994627 width=800 height=612 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the classic Sandboxels browser game on Steam with extra perks:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Workshop support - Browse and publish saves directly in-game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlimited save file management - No more save slots!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No advertisements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bigger screen space</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rich Presence for Discord</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Support the developer!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are thousands of interactions between the many materials, plants, animals, fluids, and powders in the game. Experiment with chemistry, cook food, grow an ecosystem, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simply click or use your touchscreen to select a category, like <strong>Liquids</strong>, then pick an element, like <strong>Water</strong>. Drag on the canvas above to place your pixels, and watch them interact with others!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664820/extras/7bcbf6070dfa0a5c85afd0716810cb34.avif?t=1772994627\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664820/extras_big/7bcbf6070dfa0a5c85afd0716810cb34.avif?t=1772994627 width=800 height=258 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sandboxels</strong> is a  falling-sand game featuring heat simulation, electricity, density, chemical reactions, cooking, and fire spread. With over 500 unique elements to play with, Sandboxels is a great simulator to pass the time and relax.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664820/extras/57b5c3c1b485bedf31fe9ff30515c73b.avif?t=1772994627\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664820/extras_big/57b5c3c1b485bedf31fe9ff30515c73b.avif?t=1772994627 width=800 height=612 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the classic Sandboxels browser game on Steam with extra perks:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Workshop support - Browse and publish saves directly in-game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlimited save file management - No more save slots!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No advertisements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bigger screen space</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rich Presence for Discord</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Support the developer!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are thousands of interactions between the many materials, plants, animals, fluids, and powders in the game. Experiment with chemistry, cook food, grow an ecosystem, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simply click or use your touchscreen to select a category, like <strong>Liquids</strong>, then pick an element, like <strong>Water</strong>. Drag on the canvas above to place your pixels, and watch them interact with others!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664820/extras/7bcbf6070dfa0a5c85afd0716810cb34.avif?t=1772994627\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664820/extras_big/7bcbf6070dfa0a5c85afd0716810cb34.avif?t=1772994627 width=800 height=258 /></span></p>",
